The paper proposes an automatic scoring algorithm for HER-2 in breast cancer images using color features. This involves image analysis and machine learning techniques, which are commonly associated with computer vision (cs.CV), information retrieval (cs.IR), deep learning (cs.DL), and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of color features suggests that the paper may also be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
